{
  "chapter": 39,
  "chapter_summary": "春将去，王动养伤后更懒，整天躺在竹椅上。郭大路最近总躲着燕七，王动察觉有异。郭大路向王动倾诉心事——他对燕七产生了超越友谊的感情，为此痛苦不堪，自称得了\"相思病\"。王动起初戏谑试探，得知真相后虽觉意外，却也并未嘲笑，反而帮郭大路分析燕七的种种可疑之处：睡觉拴门、偷偷溜走、衣服脏破屋子却干净，暗示燕七可能是魔教中人。郭大路决定与王动演一场吵架戏，借机离开山庄，暗中跟踪燕七查探其秘密。\n\n与此同时，林太平在山中救下一名被彪形大汉追骗的卖花姑娘。姑娘对林太平心生好感，赠花而去。次日清晨，林太平站在院中发怔，郭大路打趣他\"春天跟着小姑娘走了\"。此时卖花姑娘的歌声传来，林太平被郭大路推出门外与姑娘相会。\n\n然而燕七已不辞而别，房间里空无一人，随身物品也全部带走。郭大路质问王动是否泄露了心事，王动否认。郭大路留下\"不找到他，绝不回来\"的话后也离开了富贵山庄。富贵山庄少了笑声，王动与红娘子、林太平在屋檐下看夏雨，感叹春天真的已经过去了。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "最近你好像变得比我还懒。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁规定只有你才能最懒的？我能不能比你懒一点？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么不能？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为你最近本该比谁都有劲。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还记不记得那天燕七说你的话？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不记得。他说的话我为什么一定要记得？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们都有好师傅，我没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他说的话，也许连他自己都不相信。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但我相信，因为我的看法也跟他一样。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你武功虽然不如我们，但是和人交手时，却能随机应变，制敌机先，若套句老话来说，你正是个天赋异禀，百载难遇的练武好材料，所以……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我们应该打一架来试试看，对不对？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为……因为我有病。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你有病？什么病？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一种奇怪的病。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你以前为什么没有说起过？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为我……我不能说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯，好像有那么一点。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那就因为我有病。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知不知道你的毛病在哪里？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就在这里。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你得的是心病？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好朋友是不是应该互相保守秘密？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然应该。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你得的难道是……是花柳病？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是……可是……我这相思病，并不是为女人得的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要不是我，就没有关系了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是不是小林？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你见了活鬼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实我早就已看了出来，你老是喜欢跟他在一起。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "以前我还没有觉得什么不对，还以为那只不过因为我们是好朋友，但后来……后来……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "后来怎么样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "后来……后来就不对了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么地方不对？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有何不一样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不一样就是不一样，反正……反正就是不一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还不丢人？像我这样一个男子汉，居然……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有这种毛病的人，你也不是第一个。断袖分桃，连皇帝老子都有这种嗜好，而且千古传为佳话，我看倒不如索性跟他……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他有什么不对？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "邪气？什么邪气？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你的意思，难道是说他……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我什么都没有说，也没有说他是魔教的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "魔教……魔教……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么地方奇怪？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这几对夫妻，丈夫是男人，太太也是男人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么帮法？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想法子大吵一架。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大吵一架？怎么吵法？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "随便怎么吵都没关系，吵得越厉害越好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么要吵？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为吵过之后我就可以一走了之。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实你也不必要走，其实他……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "然后呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为什么不在家里等？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为我若就这样跟踪他，一定会被他发觉的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道你想到山下去易容改扮？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你懂得易容术？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不懂，但我却有我的法子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你既然已决心要这么做，也未尝不可，只不过……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只不过怎么样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们要吵，就得吵得像个样子，否则他绝不会相信的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要等什么样的机会呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为你本来就常常不说人话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在我只担心一件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "担心什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只怕他帮着你跟我吵，吵完了跟着你一起走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这点你倒用不着担心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我既然能跟你吵，难道就不能跟他吵么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "救命呀……救命！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "救命",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "英雄救美",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "救命",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么好事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_biao_xing_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "彪形大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老子在干的什么事，你小子难道看不出？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你放心，现在已经没有人敢欺负你了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_biao_xing_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "彪形大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道你这个兔崽子还想多管闲事不成？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好像是的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "骨碌碌",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那就得看这位姑娘的意思了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "滚吧，滚得越快越好，越远越好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "多谢这位公子相救，否则……否则……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_hua_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卖花姑娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "多……多谢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你一个小姑娘家，怎么会跟那种人到这种地方来的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你这一篮子花，共值多少钱？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_hua_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卖花姑娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三……三……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，我就给你三两银子，这一篮花我全买下来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎么不说话呀？难道是个哑巴？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这小姑娘胆子真小。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只不过问了她两句话而已，又没有怎么样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我又不是自己要问。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你替谁问？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "早。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看来好像有点心事，究竟在想什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我在想……春天好像已经过去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，春天已经过去了，昨天刚过去的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "昨天过去的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你能不能少说几句缺德话？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我这话难道就错了么？你难道不想将春天留住？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 572
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "出去干什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 602,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "太阳已经晒在头上了，还不起来？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 638,
      "line_end": 638
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他不在后面院子，也不在厨房。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 644,
      "line_end": 644
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看样子他好像是昨天晚上走的。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 660,
      "line_end": 660
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 662,
      "line_end": 662
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你想我会告诉他什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 672,
      "line_end": 672
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我跟你说的那些话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 674,
      "line_end": 674
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你以为我是那种人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 676,
      "line_end": 676
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你真的什么都没有说？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 678,
      "line_end": 678
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你自己刚才也说过，这次不同。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 690,
      "line_end": 690
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是他根本没有原因要不辞而别。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 692,
      "line_end": 692
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实你们根本也并没有什么不对劲。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 698,
      "line_end": 698
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还没有？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 700,
      "line_end": 700
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实他……他……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 702,
      "line_end": 702
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他怎么样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 704,
      "line_end": 704
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没怎么样，没怎么样……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 706,
      "line_end": 706
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你到哪里去？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 710,
      "line_end": 710
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "去找杯酒喝喝。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 712,
      "line_end": 712
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他到哪里去了？为什么一句话都不留下？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 736,
      "line_end": 736
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不找到他，我绝不回来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 742,
      "line_end": 742
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在虽已过去了，但很快就会再来的。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 764,
      "line_end": 764
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，春天无论去多远，都一定会回来的。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 766,
      "line_end": 766
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一定？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 768,
      "line_end": 768
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一定。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 770,
      "line_end": 770
    }
  ],
